Dialogue: 8,0:00:11.37,0:00:14.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,这就是小朝的理想型啊
Dialogue: 7,0:00:11.37,0:00:14.24,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝はこういう人が好みなんだ
Dialogue: 8,0:00:18.94,0:00:20.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我是爱听他们的歌
Dialogue: 7,0:00:18.94,0:00:20.50,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,曲が好きなの
Dialogue: 8,0:00:22.50,0:00:24.13,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我懂
Dialogue: 7,0:00:22.50,0:00:24.13,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,分かる
Dialogue: 8,0:00:24.13,0:00:26.35,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,爸妈就爱说这种话
Dialogue: 7,0:00:24.13,0:00:26.35,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,親ってそういうこと言うよね
Dialogue: 8,0:00:26.35,0:00:29.27,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我看演唱会  又不是想和他们谈恋爱
Dialogue: 7,0:00:26.35,0:00:29.27,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,付き合いたいとか思って見てないっつうの
Dialogue: 8,0:00:29.27,0:00:30.64,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 7,0:00:29.27,0:00:30.64,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ねえ
Dialogue: 8,0:00:30.64,0:00:33.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我不是喜欢女团偶像吗
Dialogue: 7,0:00:30.64,0:00:33.24,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,うちも女の子好きじゃん　アイドル
Dialogue: 8,0:00:33.24,0:00:37.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,爸妈就觉得  我看这些是因为我想当偶像
Dialogue: 7,0:00:33.24,0:00:37.37,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私がアイドルになりたくて見てると思ってる節があるの
Dialogue: 8,0:00:37.37,0:00:38.72,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,真逗
Dialogue: 7,0:00:37.37,0:00:38.72,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ウケる
Dialogue: 8,0:00:38.72,0:00:40.52,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,完全搞不清状况
Dialogue: 7,0:00:38.72,0:00:40.52,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,マジ分かってない
Dialogue: 8,0:00:40.52,0:00:43.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,感觉爸妈还有老师  都挺矛盾的
Dialogue: 7,0:00:40.52,0:00:43.86,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なんか矛盾してるんだよね　親とか先生って
Dialogue: 8,0:00:43.86,0:00:45.08,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 7,0:00:43.86,0:00:45.08,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ねー
Dialogue: 8,0:00:45.08,0:00:45.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 7,0:00:45.08,0:00:45.65,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 8,0:00:46.37,0:00:48.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,想做什么就尽管去做吧
Dialogue: 7,0:00:46.37,0:00:48.96,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,やりたいことはなんでもやっていいから
Dialogue: 8,0:00:49.62,0:00:52.03,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你要做你想做的人
Dialogue: 7,0:00:49.62,0:00:52.03,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なりたいものになりなさい
Dialogue: 8,0:00:52.24,0:00:54.05,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我长大后才不要变成他们那样
Dialogue: 7,0:00:52.24,0:00:54.05,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ああいう大人になりたくない
Dialogue: 8,0:00:54.05,0:00:55.29,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 7,0:00:54.05,0:00:55.29,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,だよね
Dialogue: 8,0:00:55.79,0:00:59.16,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妈妈会永远支持你的
Dialogue: 7,0:00:55.79,0:00:59.16,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お母さん　いつでも味方だから
Dialogue: 8,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,好吗  朝
Dialogue: 7,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.42,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ねっ　朝
Dialogue: 8,0:01:09.03,0:01:12.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,朝  回来的时候买点厕纸呗
Dialogue: 7,0:01:09.03,0:01:12.96,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ねえ　帰りにトイレットペーパー買ってきてくれる？
Dialogue: 8,0:01:12.96,0:01:14.30,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 7,0:01:12.96,0:01:14.30,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,はーい
Dialogue: 8,0:01:17.88,0:01:20.06,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我妈也是这副样子
Dialogue: 7,0:01:17.88,0:01:20.06,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お母さんもそうだった
Dialogue: 8,0:01:20.06,0:01:23.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我出门前  她总是这个姿势
Dialogue: 7,0:01:20.06,0:01:23.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,出かける前にいつもそのポーズ
Dialogue: 8,0:01:24.99,0:01:27.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,可能随我妈了
Dialogue: 7,0:01:24.99,0:01:27.42,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,母がそうだったのかも
Dialogue: 8,0:01:27.42,0:01:30.06,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我能染个头发吗
Dialogue: 7,0:01:27.42,0:01:30.06,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ねえ　髪染めていい？
Dialogue: 8,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.20,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 7,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.20,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 8,0:01:31.20,0:01:33.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,昨天绘美里建议我试试
Dialogue: 7,0:01:31.20,0:01:33.57,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,昨日　えみりが勧めてくれて
Dialogue: 8,0:01:33.57,0:01:35.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我不是说这个
Dialogue: 7,0:01:33.57,0:01:35.87,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いや　じゃなくて
Dialogue: 8,0:01:35.87,0:01:38.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你染发不用问我同不同意
Dialogue: 7,0:01:35.87,0:01:38.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私の許可取ることじゃないでしょう
Dialogue: 8,0:01:39.24,0:01:41.79,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,只要不违反校规  你想染就染
Dialogue: 7,0:01:39.24,0:01:41.79,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,校則が大丈夫なら　やれば？
Dialogue: 8,0:01:48.75,0:01:51.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你是田汲吧
Dialogue: 7,0:01:48.75,0:01:51.22,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,田汲さんだっけ？
Dialogue: 8,0:01:51.22,0:01:52.97,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,咱俩同班的
Dialogue: 7,0:01:51.22,0:01:52.97,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,同じクラス
Dialogue: 8,0:01:52.97,0:01:55.20,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,森  叫我朝就行
Dialogue: 7,0:01:52.97,0:01:55.20,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,森さん　朝でいいよ
Dialogue: 8,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.08,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你也直接叫我森吧
Dialogue: 7,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.08,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あたしも森でいいっす
Dialogue: 8,0:01:58.08,0:01:59.72,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,定了吗
Dialogue: 7,0:01:58.08,0:01:59.72,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,決めた？
Dialogue: 8,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,还没  你呢
Dialogue: 7,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.91,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,んーん　朝は？
Dialogue: 8,0:02:01.91,0:02:03.67,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我也没
Dialogue: 7,0:02:01.91,0:02:03.67,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いやあ
Dialogue: 8,0:02:03.67,0:02:05.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你初中那会儿进了什么社团
Dialogue: 7,0:02:03.67,0:02:05.86,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,中学のときはなんかやってた？
Dialogue: 8,0:02:05.86,0:02:06.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,合唱团
Dialogue: 7,0:02:05.86,0:02:06.86,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,合唱
Dialogue: 8,0:02:06.86,0:02:08.48,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,这个好呀
Dialogue: 7,0:02:06.86,0:02:08.48,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いいじゃん
Dialogue: 8,0:02:08.48,0:02:11.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,听说咱们高中的合唱团很强
Dialogue: 7,0:02:08.48,0:02:11.36,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ここ　強いらしいよ　合唱
Dialogue: 8,0:02:11.36,0:02:13.23,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你选好了吗
Dialogue: 7,0:02:11.36,0:02:13.23,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,選択　決めた？
Dialogue: 8,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,还没
Dialogue: 7,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.49,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,まだ
Dialogue: 8,0:02:14.73,0:02:16.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,其实进哪个社团都一样
Dialogue: 7,0:02:14.73,0:02:16.96,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,別にどっちでもいいんだけどさあ
Dialogue: 8,0:02:16.96,0:02:18.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 7,0:02:16.96,0:02:18.39,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,俺も
Dialogue: 8,0:02:20.71,0:02:23.54,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,大家都是怎么选的呀
Dialogue: 7,0:02:20.71,0:02:23.54,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,みんな　どうやって決めてんだろ
Dialogue: 8,0:02:23.54,0:02:25.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,没有想做的事吗
Dialogue: 7,0:02:23.54,0:02:25.50,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,やりたいのないの？
Dialogue: 8,0:02:26.91,0:02:30.00,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妈妈以前是羽毛球社的
Dialogue: 7,0:02:26.91,0:02:30.00,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お母さんはバドミントン部だったけど
Dialogue: 8,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.54,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不喜欢
Dialogue: 7,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.54,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ちがーう
Dialogue: 8,0:02:31.54,0:02:33.00,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不喜欢啊
Dialogue: 7,0:02:31.54,0:02:33.00,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そうかあ
Dialogue: 8,0:02:34.51,0:02:35.95,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,那合唱团呢
Dialogue: 7,0:02:34.51,0:02:35.95,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,合唱は？
Dialogue: 8,0:02:35.95,0:02:37.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你喜欢唱歌吧
Dialogue: 7,0:02:35.95,0:02:37.76,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝　歌好きでしょ
Dialogue: 8,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,四年级那会儿举办合唱比赛
Dialogue: 7,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.36,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ほら　4{\fscx50} {\fscx100}年生のときのコンクール
Dialogue: 8,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.11,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你当时可拼了
Dialogue: 7,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.11,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,頑張ってたじゃない
Dialogue: 8,0:02:42.11,0:02:43.77,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,合唱团啊
Dialogue: 7,0:02:42.11,0:02:43.77,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,合唱か
Dialogue: 8,0:02:43.77,0:02:45.15,Dial-CHI,,0,500,0,,那就决定了
Dialogue: 7,0:02:43.77,0:02:45.15,Dial-JPN,,0,500,0,,決まりね
Dialogue: 8,0:02:45.15,0:02:47.77,Dial-CHI,,0,500,0,,听妈妈的准没错
Dialogue: 7,0:02:45.15,0:02:47.77,Dial-JPN,,0,500,0,,お母さん　間違いないんだから
Dialogue: 8,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,穿那件有格子纹的吧
Dialogue: 7,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.65,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,チェックのほうじゃない？
Dialogue: 8,0:02:51.65,0:02:54.90,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不行  昨天吃的就是番茄味
Dialogue: 7,0:02:51.65,0:02:54.90,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ダメ　昨日もトマト味でした
Dialogue: 8,0:02:55.51,0:02:57.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你还在纠结吗
Dialogue: 7,0:02:55.51,0:02:57.45,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,まだ迷ってるの？
Dialogue: 8,0:02:57.45,0:02:59.66,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,那妈妈来帮你选吧
Dialogue: 7,0:02:57.45,0:02:59.66,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　お母さん　決めてあげる
Dialogue: 8,0:03:00.02,0:03:02.16,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不是那个
Dialogue: 7,0:03:00.02,0:03:02.16,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そっちじゃないよ　朝
Dialogue: 8,0:03:02.56,0:03:06.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你得学会自己拿主意
Dialogue: 7,0:03:02.56,0:03:06.17,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なんでも自分で決められるようにならないと
Dialogue: 8,0:03:06.52,0:03:09.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,天呐  这头发怎么搞的
Dialogue: 7,0:03:06.52,0:03:09.17,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,やだ　どうしたの　その髪
Dialogue: 8,0:03:09.48,0:03:11.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,跟个假小子似的
Dialogue: 7,0:03:09.48,0:03:11.50,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,男の子みたいじゃない
Dialogue: 8,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.67,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,太可爱了吧
Dialogue: 7,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.67,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,超かわいい
Dialogue: 8,0:03:14.67,0:03:16.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,朝  真的很好看
Dialogue: 7,0:03:14.67,0:03:16.62,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,かわいいよ　朝
Dialogue: 8,0:03:16.62,0:03:19.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,也就你会这么夸我了
Dialogue: 7,0:03:16.62,0:03:19.18,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,えみりだけだよ　それ言ってくれるの
Dialogue: 8,0:03:19.18,0:03:21.99,Dial-CHI,,32,0,0,,是吗  你爸妈不喜欢？
Dialogue: 7,0:03:19.18,0:03:21.99,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,えー　親　反対してるの？
Dialogue: 8,0:03:21.99,0:03:23.05,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 7,0:03:21.99,0:03:23.05,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,みたい
Dialogue: 8,0:03:23.05,0:03:25.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,只能想办法让他们接受了
Dialogue: 7,0:03:23.05,0:03:25.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,まあ　分からせるしかないね
Dialogue: 8,0:03:26.08,0:03:27.16,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,怎么做
Dialogue: 7,0:03:26.08,0:03:27.16,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どうやって
Dialogue: 8,0:03:27.91,0:03:30.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,总之  趁着放春假
Dialogue: 7,0:03:27.91,0:03:30.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,とりあえず　春休みの間に
Dialogue: 8,0:03:34.87,0:03:35.45,Dial-CHI-TOP,,30,0,0,,出车祸了？
Dialogue: 7,0:03:34.87,0:03:35.45,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,事故？
Dialogue: 8,0:03:35.45,0:03:36.17,Dial-CHI-TOP,,30,0,0,,报警了？
Dialogue: 7,0:03:35.45,0:03:36.17,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,警察？
Dialogue: 8,0:03:36.17,0:03:36.97,Dial-CHI-TOP,,30,0,0,,叫救护车？
Dialogue: 7,0:03:36.17,0:03:36.97,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,救急車？
Dialogue: 8,0:03:36.97,0:03:38.15,Dial-CHI-TOP,,0,0,0,,车根本没法往外开啊
Dialogue: 7,0:03:36.97,0:03:38.15,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,車　出せないじゃん
Dialogue: 8,0:03:38.15,0:03:40.03,Dial-CHI-TOP,,0,0,0,,谁快去叫一下店员
Dialogue: 7,0:03:38.15,0:03:40.03,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,誰か　店の人呼んで
Dialogue: 8,0:03:41.71,0:03:44.95,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,也是  很难一下子就打定主意
Dialogue: 7,0:03:41.71,0:03:44.95,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,まあ　急に決めろとか言われてもね
Dialogue: 8,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,回见
Dialogue: 7,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,じゃあね
Dialogue: 8,0:03:49.30,0:03:52.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,怎么回事  总觉得很生气
Dialogue: 7,0:03:49.30,0:03:52.86,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なんだろう　なんか腹が立つ
Dialogue: 8,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我在气什么
Dialogue: 7,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.21,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,何に？
Dialogue: 8,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.03,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,搞不懂
Dialogue: 7,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.03,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,分かんない
Dialogue: 8,0:03:57.47,0:03:59.47,Dial-CHI-TOP,,0,0,0,,缝纫机给干冒烟了
Dialogue: 7,0:03:57.47,0:03:59.47,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,ミシンから煙出てた
Dialogue: 8,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.04,Dial-CHI-TOP,,30,0,0,,还有这种事？
Dialogue: 7,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.04,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,そんなことある？
Dialogue: 8,0:04:02.04,0:04:02.72,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,绘美理
Dialogue: 7,0:04:02.04,0:04:02.72,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,えみり
Dialogue: 8,0:04:02.04,0:04:02.72,Dial-CHI-TOP,,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 7,0:04:02.04,0:04:02.72,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,ウソー
Dialogue: 8,0:04:02.72,0:04:03.81,Dial-CHI-TOP,,0,0,0,,千真万确
Dialogue: 7,0:04:02.72,0:04:03.81,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,マジマジ
Dialogue: 8,0:04:03.81,0:04:04.86,Dial-CHI-TOP,,0,0,0,,要赔吗
Dialogue: 7,0:04:03.81,0:04:04.86,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,弁償？
Dialogue: 8,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.23,Dial-CHI-TOP,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 7,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.23,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,どうだろ
Dialogue: 8,0:04:10.23,0:04:12.48,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你妈现在已经不在了
Dialogue: 7,0:04:10.23,0:04:12.48,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,もういないじゃん　お母さん
Dialogue: 8,0:04:13.61,0:04:14.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 7,0:04:13.61,0:04:14.86,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 8,0:04:15.99,0:04:18.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你要做你想做的人
Dialogue: 7,0:04:15.99,0:04:18.24,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なりたいものになりなさい
Dialogue: 8,0:04:19.89,0:04:21.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,骗子
Dialogue: 7,0:04:19.89,0:04:21.12,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ウソつき
Dialogue: 8,0:04:21.56,0:04:23.53,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妈妈会永远…
Dialogue: 7,0:04:21.56,0:04:23.53,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お母さんはいつでも…
Dialogue: 8,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,自相矛盾
Dialogue: 7,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.62,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,矛盾してる
Dialogue: 8,0:04:26.72,0:04:29.00,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我好生气
Dialogue: 7,0:04:26.72,0:04:29.00,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ムカつく
Dialogue: 8,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.30,Dial-CHI,,1200,0,0,,高代槙生
Dialogue: 7,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.30,Dial-JPN,,1200,0,0,,こうだい槙生
Dialogue: 8,0:06:11.31,0:06:12.69,Dial-CHI,,1100,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 7,0:06:11.31,0:06:12.69,Dial-JPN,,1100,0,0,,すご
Dialogue: 8,0:06:24.70,0:06:27.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,这周六去外婆家
Dialogue: 7,0:06:24.70,0:06:27.21,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,おばあちゃんち　今度の土曜
Dialogue: 8,0:06:27.21,0:06:28.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你想去吗
Dialogue: 7,0:06:27.21,0:06:28.57,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,行きたいの？
Dialogue: 8,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我打了个电话
Dialogue: 7,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,電話したら
Dialogue: 8,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,她还挺担心我的
Dialogue: 7,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.86,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,心配してくれてたし
Dialogue: 8,0:06:31.86,0:06:35.03,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,毕竟我和我妈经常去看她
Dialogue: 7,0:06:31.86,0:06:35.03,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,前はよく行ってたから　お母さんと
Dialogue: 8,0:06:35.03,0:06:37.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我得有五年多没回去了
Dialogue: 7,0:06:35.03,0:06:37.21,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,5{\fscx50} {\fscx100}年以上　帰ってないかも
Dialogue: 8,0:06:37.57,0:06:38.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 7,0:06:37.57,0:06:38.63,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 8,0:06:39.41,0:06:40.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,没啥原因
Dialogue: 7,0:06:39.41,0:06:40.84,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なんとなく
Dialogue: 8,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.97,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,行  那就去吧
Dialogue: 7,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.97,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いいよ　行こうか
Dialogue: 8,0:06:44.56,0:06:48.35,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,哎哟  你来啦  小朝
Dialogue: 7,0:06:44.56,0:06:48.35,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,まあまあ　いらっしゃい　朝ちゃん
Dialogue: 8,0:06:48.35,0:06:50.55,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你有好好照顾她吗
Dialogue: 7,0:06:48.35,0:06:50.55,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ちゃんとやれてるの？
Dialogue: 8,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.67,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,有吧
Dialogue: 7,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.67,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,まあ
Dialogue: 8,0:06:51.67,0:06:52.35,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,快进来
Dialogue: 7,0:06:51.67,0:06:52.35,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 8,0:06:52.35,0:06:55.05,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,喝杯茶  再吃点蛋糕
Dialogue: 7,0:06:52.35,0:06:55.05,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お茶にしましょう　ケーキあるから
Dialogue: 8,0:06:55.05,0:06:56.77,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,打扰啦
Dialogue: 7,0:06:55.05,0:06:56.77,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お邪魔しまーす
Dialogue: 8,0:06:57.61,0:07:00.16,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我先去收拾行李了
Dialogue: 7,0:06:57.61,0:07:00.16,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私　先に荷物の整理を
Dialogue: 8,0:07:00.86,0:07:03.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,急什么  喝杯茶再去呗
Dialogue: 7,0:07:00.86,0:07:03.96,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なあに　お茶の{\fscx50} {\fscx100}1{\fscx50} {\fscx100}杯くらい
Dialogue: 8,0:07:03.96,0:07:05.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,喝着喝着时间就过去了
Dialogue: 7,0:07:03.96,0:07:05.86,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,その{\fscx50} {\fscx100}1{\fscx50} {\fscx100}杯が長くなるから
Dialogue: 8,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.98,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我要是渴了  等会自己倒
Dialogue: 7,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.98,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,飲みたくなったら　あとで自分でやります
Dialogue: 8,0:07:08.98,0:07:11.60,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你看你小姨  真冷漠
Dialogue: 7,0:07:08.98,0:07:11.60,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,まあ　叔母さん　薄情でしょ
Dialogue: 8,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.28,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你可别学她
Dialogue: 7,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.28,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,見習っちゃダメよ
Dialogue: 8,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,来  快进来吧
Dialogue: 7,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.87,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,さあ　来て来て　ほら
Dialogue: 8,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.60,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,这种幼稚的书  你打算看到几岁啊
Dialogue: 7,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.60,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いつまでそんな子どもっぽいもの読んでるの？
Dialogue: 8,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你前阵子不还在看吗
Dialogue: 7,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.71,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,自分だってこないだまで読んでたじゃん
Dialogue: 8,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我说我不看了
Dialogue: 7,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.87,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,もう読まないっつってんの
Dialogue: 8,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 7,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.02,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,はあ
Dialogue: 8,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.61,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,那以后甭想让我借给你
Dialogue: 7,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.61,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,じゃあ二度と貸さないから
Dialogue: 8,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.32,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 7,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.32,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,結構です
Dialogue: 8,0:07:51.75,0:07:55.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,真头疼  想起了好多往事
Dialogue: 7,0:07:51.75,0:07:55.50,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,困るな　いろいろ思い出して
Dialogue: 8,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.29,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是不是走右边
Dialogue: 7,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.29,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ねえ　右じゃない？
Dialogue: 8,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.29,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,肯定有密道
Dialogue: 7,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.29,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,絶対隠し通路ある
Dialogue: 8,0:08:03.72,0:08:05.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,敌人来了
Dialogue: 7,0:08:03.72,0:08:05.01,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,敵　来てる
Dialogue: 8,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.23,Dial-CHI,,0,475,0,,敌人  快看快看
Dialogue: 7,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.23,Dial-JPN,,0,475,0,,敵　ほら　ほら
Dialogue: 8,0:08:05.28,0:08:07.25,Dial-CHI,,650,0,0,,姐姐  你好吵
Dialogue: 7,0:08:05.28,0:08:07.25,Dial-JPN,,650,0,0,,お姉ちゃん　うるさい
Dialogue: 8,0:08:06.23,0:08:07.25,Dial-CHI,,0,475,0,,快  右边右边
Dialogue: 7,0:08:06.23,0:08:07.25,Dial-JPN,,0,475,0,,ほら　右右右
Dialogue: 8,0:08:06.75,0:08:10.31,Dial-CHI-TOP,,0,0,0,,你们两个  离电视远点
Dialogue: 7,0:08:06.75,0:08:10.31,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,2{\fscx50} {\fscx100}人とも　テレビから離れなさい
Dialogue: 8,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,打中了打中了
Dialogue: 7,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.31,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,当たる　当たる
Dialogue: 8,0:08:11.76,0:08:15.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,大学想好考哪了吗
Dialogue: 7,0:08:11.76,0:08:15.15,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,大学は？もう決めたの？
Dialogue: 8,0:08:15.15,0:08:17.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,这才刚上高中呢  外婆
Dialogue: 7,0:08:15.15,0:08:17.78,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,まだ入ったばっかだよ　おばあちゃん
Dialogue: 8,0:08:17.78,0:08:20.88,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,哦  这样啊  也对
Dialogue: 7,0:08:17.78,0:08:20.88,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ああ　そうか　そうよね
Dialogue: 8,0:08:20.88,0:08:24.00,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,主要是实里和槙生很早就定了
Dialogue: 7,0:08:20.88,0:08:24.00,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,実里も槙生も早かったから　ついね
Dialogue: 8,0:08:24.66,0:08:25.98,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我妈也是吗
Dialogue: 7,0:08:24.66,0:08:25.98,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お母さんも？
Dialogue: 8,0:08:27.13,0:08:31.48,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,实里那孩子特别听我的话
Dialogue: 7,0:08:27.13,0:08:31.48,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,実里は　私の話もよく聞いてくれる子でね
Dialogue: 8,0:08:31.48,0:08:34.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我们经常一起聊天
Dialogue: 7,0:08:31.48,0:08:34.12,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,よくおしゃべりしたわね
Dialogue: 8,0:08:34.12,0:08:36.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,槙生就不一样了
Dialogue: 7,0:08:34.12,0:08:36.04,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,その点　あの子は
Dialogue: 8,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.06,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我去帮槙生姨收拾东西
Dialogue: 7,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.06,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,槙生ちゃん　手伝ってくる
Dialogue: 8,0:08:43.19,0:08:45.05,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,再坐一会儿呗
Dialogue: 7,0:08:43.19,0:08:45.05,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,もう少しゆっくりすれば
Dialogue: 8,0:08:45.05,0:08:46.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,马上就回来
Dialogue: 7,0:08:45.05,0:08:46.63,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,すぐ戻る
Dialogue: 8,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,槙生姨
Dialogue: 7,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.56,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,槙生ちゃん
Dialogue: 8,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.31,Dial-CHI,,1200,0,0,,妈…
Dialogue: 7,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.31,Dial-JPN,,1200,0,0,,おかっ
Dialogue: 8,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.06,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 7,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.06,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 8,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 7,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.31,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 8,0:09:03.94,0:09:06.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你来过我姐的房间吧
Dialogue: 7,0:09:03.94,0:09:06.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,姉さんの部屋　来たことあるでしょ
Dialogue: 8,0:09:07.20,0:09:10.11,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,有什么想要的  就带回去吧
Dialogue: 7,0:09:07.20,0:09:10.11,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,欲しいものがあるなら　持っていけば？
Dialogue: 8,0:09:13.68,0:09:16.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你和我妈聊了些什么
Dialogue: 7,0:09:13.68,0:09:16.91,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,何か話したの　うちの母と
Dialogue: 8,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 7,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.12,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,特に
Dialogue: 8,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 7,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.33,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 8,0:09:19.33,0:09:23.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,槙生姨  你也讨厌外婆吗
Dialogue: 7,0:09:19.33,0:09:23.57,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,槙生ちゃんは　おばあちゃんのことも嫌いなの？
Dialogue: 8,0:09:23.57,0:09:26.79,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我怎么可能见谁都讨厌
Dialogue: 7,0:09:23.57,0:09:26.79,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,誰でも嫌いなわけでは
Dialogue: 8,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.47,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,也不知道从什么时候起
Dialogue: 7,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.47,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,まあ　でもいつからか
Dialogue: 8,0:09:29.47,0:09:33.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,她人变笨了  又多了些小聪明
Dialogue: 7,0:09:29.47,0:09:33.22,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あの人は鈍くて　ずるい人になってしまった
Dialogue: 8,0:09:33.63,0:09:36.78,Dial-CHI-TOP,,0,0,0,,也许是因为我们离开了家  加上父亲去世了
Dialogue: 7,0:09:33.63,0:09:36.78,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,私たちが家を出て　父も死んで
Dialogue: 8,0:09:36.78,0:09:39.80,Dial-CHI-TOP,,0,0,0,,她总是一个人待着
Dialogue: 7,0:09:36.78,0:09:39.80,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,1{\fscx50} {\fscx100}人でいる時間が増えたせいかもしれない
Dialogue: 8,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.98,Dial-CHI,,0,500,0,,人变笨了  耍小聪明
Dialogue: 7,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.98,Dial-JPN,,0,500,0,,鈍くて　ずるい
Dialogue: 8,0:09:43.23,0:09:46.88,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,以前她常说  实里懂事会照顾人
Dialogue: 7,0:09:43.23,0:09:46.88,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,昔はよく　実里は気配りができて
Dialogue: 8,0:09:46.88,0:09:50.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,槙生懂得自力更生
Dialogue: 7,0:09:46.88,0:09:50.17,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,槙生は自立してると言ってくれてたの
Dialogue: 8,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,然而后来改口了
Dialogue: 7,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.92,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,それがいつの間にか
Dialogue: 8,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,说实里没有主见
Dialogue: 7,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.80,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,実里は自主性がなく
Dialogue: 8,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,槙生冷漠无情
Dialogue: 7,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.49,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,槙生は薄情と言いかえるようになった
Dialogue: 8,0:09:57.27,0:10:00.53,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,这让我挺伤心的
Dialogue: 7,0:09:57.27,0:10:00.53,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,それが私は悲しかった
Dialogue: 8,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,可是  外婆她
Dialogue: 7,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.50,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,でも　おばあちゃん
Dialogue: 8,0:10:02.50,0:10:06.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,怎么能让白发人送黑发人啊
Dialogue: 7,0:10:02.50,0:10:06.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,親より先に死ぬ子がありますか
Dialogue: 8,0:10:06.19,0:10:08.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,哭得特别伤心
Dialogue: 7,0:10:06.19,0:10:08.37,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,すごく泣いてた
Dialogue: 8,0:10:08.37,0:10:11.26,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我觉得外婆她其实
Dialogue: 7,0:10:08.37,0:10:11.26,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,大事に思ってたんだなって思ったよ
Dialogue: 8,0:10:11.26,0:10:13.05,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,特别在乎我妈
Dialogue: 7,0:10:11.26,0:10:13.05,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お母さんのこと
Dialogue: 8,0:10:13.83,0:10:16.54,Dial-CHI,,0,500,0,,你愿意这么想  也挺好的
Dialogue: 7,0:10:13.83,0:10:16.54,Dial-JPN,,0,500,0,,あなたがそう思うなら　それでいい
Dialogue: 8,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.85,Dial-CHI,,0,500,0,,我妈妈
Dialogue: 7,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.85,Dial-JPN,,0,500,0,,お母さんって
Dialogue: 8,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,究竟是个怎样的人
Dialogue: 7,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.22,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どんな人だったんだろう
Dialogue: 8,0:10:22.33,0:10:25.61,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,心里又在想些什么
Dialogue: 7,0:10:22.33,0:10:25.61,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,何を考えてたんだろう
Dialogue: 8,0:10:26.03,0:10:31.10,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,就算她人还在  我们也无从得知
Dialogue: 7,0:10:26.03,0:10:31.10,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,それは生きてたとしても分かりようがないことだね
Dialogue: 8,0:10:31.10,0:10:33.90,Dial-CHI,,32,0,0,,因为人跟人不一样？
Dialogue: 7,0:10:31.10,0:10:33.90,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,違う人間だから？
Dialogue: 8,0:10:35.24,0:10:36.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 7,0:10:35.24,0:10:36.24,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 8,0:10:37.59,0:10:40.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你继续喜欢你妈妈就好
Dialogue: 7,0:10:37.59,0:10:40.71,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お母さんのことを好きなままでいなさい
Dialogue: 8,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,为此
Dialogue: 7,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.62,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そのために
Dialogue: 8,0:10:43.62,0:10:46.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我不会和你聊我的个人偏见
Dialogue: 7,0:10:43.62,0:10:46.63,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私の主観でしかない話はしないの
Dialogue: 8,0:10:49.38,0:10:51.13,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我去喝杯茶
Dialogue: 7,0:10:49.38,0:10:51.13,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お茶もらってこよ
Dialogue: 8,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.59,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,原来她喜欢这些书啊
Dialogue: 7,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.59,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,こういうのが好きなんだ
Dialogue: 8,0:11:01.50,0:11:02.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 7,0:11:01.50,0:11:02.56,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 8,0:11:02.56,0:11:06.06,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你要做你想做的人
Dialogue: 7,0:11:02.56,0:11:06.06,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なりたいものになりなさい
Dialogue: 8,0:11:07.66,0:11:10.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我会的  做理想中的自己
Dialogue: 7,0:11:07.66,0:11:10.57,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なるよ　なりたい自分に
Dialogue: 8,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.07,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你等着瞧
Dialogue: 7,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.07,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ザマアミロ
Dialogue: 8,0:11:18.37,0:11:21.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,把这个也带上  快拿着
Dialogue: 7,0:11:18.37,0:11:21.12,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,これも持っていきなさいって　ほら
Dialogue: 8,0:11:21.12,0:11:23.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,别  家里没地儿放
Dialogue: 7,0:11:21.12,0:11:23.12,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いや　置くとこないから
Dialogue: 8,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.10,Dial-CHI,,0,800,0,,听话  快拿着
Dialogue: 7,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.10,Dial-JPN,,0,800,0,,いいから　ほら
Dialogue: 8,0:11:24.00,0:11:26.74,Dial-CHI,,200,0,0,,不了不了  真不用
Dialogue: 7,0:11:24.00,0:11:26.74,Dial-JPN,,200,0,0,,いいって　いい　いい
Dialogue: 8,0:11:26.74,0:11:29.09,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你这孩子真是的
Dialogue: 7,0:11:26.74,0:11:29.09,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,まったく　あなたは
Dialogue: 8,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.72,Dial-CHI-TOP,,0,0,0,,外婆她哭得特别伤心
Dialogue: 7,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.72,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,おばあちゃん　すごく泣いてた
Dialogue: 8,0:11:32.86,0:11:35.94,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,小朝  要注意身体
Dialogue: 7,0:11:32.86,0:11:35.94,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝ちゃん　体に気をつけてね
Dialogue: 8,0:11:35.94,0:11:36.94,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 7,0:11:35.94,0:11:36.94,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いってきます
Dialogue: 8,0:11:36.94,0:11:38.75,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 7,0:11:36.94,0:11:38.75,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いってきまーす
Dialogue: 8,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.09,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 7,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.09,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いってらっしゃい
Dialogue: 8,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.72,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你俩要注意车子
Dialogue: 7,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.72,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,2{\fscx50} {\fscx100}人とも　車に気をつけて
Dialogue: 8,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.73,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,槙生你也是
Dialogue: 7,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.73,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,槙生も
Dialogue: 8,0:11:45.12,0:11:47.11,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,要注意规律作息
Dialogue: 7,0:11:45.12,0:11:47.11,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,不摂生しちゃダメよ
Dialogue: 8,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.93,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 7,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.93,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お母さん
Dialogue: 8,0:11:51.48,0:11:56.11,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我跟我姐已经不可能了
Dialogue: 7,0:11:51.48,0:11:56.11,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃんと私はもうダメだったから
Dialogue: 8,0:11:56.70,0:12:01.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,所以  我没法为您分担这份悲伤
Dialogue: 7,0:11:56.70,0:12:01.12,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,だから　お母さんと悲しさを分かち合うことはできないんだけど
Dialogue: 8,0:12:01.66,0:12:04.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不过  您要是觉得难过了
Dialogue: 7,0:12:01.66,0:12:04.37,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,でも　お母さんが悲しければ
Dialogue: 8,0:12:04.37,0:12:07.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我还是能听您发发牢骚的
Dialogue: 7,0:12:04.37,0:12:07.37,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,話を聞くくらいはできるから
Dialogue: 8,0:12:08.26,0:12:12.13,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你为什么偏要多啰嗦一句
Dialogue: 7,0:12:08.26,0:12:12.13,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どうしてあなたはそうひと言多いの
Dialogue: 8,0:12:12.13,0:12:15.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,自己都快顾不过来了
Dialogue: 7,0:12:12.13,0:12:15.01,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,自分のことで手いっぱいな人が
Dialogue: 8,0:12:15.01,0:12:18.64,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,哪还有闲心听别人发牢骚
Dialogue: 7,0:12:15.01,0:12:18.64,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,誰かの話なんて聞く余裕ないでしょうに
Dialogue: 8,0:12:19.37,0:12:23.64,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你就和小朝好好过日子吧
Dialogue: 7,0:12:19.37,0:12:23.64,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝ちゃんとよく協力して　きちんと暮らすのよ
Dialogue: 8,0:12:23.64,0:12:25.64,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您可真懂我
Dialogue: 7,0:12:23.64,0:12:25.64,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,よくお分かりで
Dialogue: 8,0:12:26.18,0:12:29.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你以为是谁把你养大的
Dialogue: 7,0:12:26.18,0:12:29.65,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,誰が育てたと思ってるの
Dialogue: 8,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不接吗
Dialogue: 7,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.39,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,出ないの
Dialogue: 8,0:12:41.39,0:12:43.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是骚扰电话
Dialogue: 7,0:12:41.39,0:12:43.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,知らない番号だから
Dialogue: 8,0:12:54.78,0:12:55.67,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 7,0:12:54.78,0:12:55.67,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 8,0:12:56.30,0:12:57.55,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 7,0:12:56.30,0:12:57.55,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,おはよ
Dialogue: 8,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 7,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.04,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,おはよ
Dialogue: 8,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你今天有体育课吗
Dialogue: 7,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.80,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ねえ　今日体育ある？
Dialogue: 8,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.98,Dial-CHI,,32,0,0,,怎么  忘带运动服了？
Dialogue: 7,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.98,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,何　ジャージ忘れた？
Dialogue: 8,0:13:02.98,0:13:04.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 7,0:13:02.98,0:13:04.31,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,イエース
Dialogue: 8,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.40,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,借你穿
Dialogue: 7,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.40,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いいよ
Dialogue: 8,0:13:05.40,0:13:07.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,谢啦
Dialogue: 7,0:13:05.40,0:13:07.24,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 8,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.48,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,话说你要参加什么社团
Dialogue: 7,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.48,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ねえ　朝は部活どうするの？
Dialogue: 8,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,楢  早上好
Dialogue: 7,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.31,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,楢ならさん　おはよ
Dialogue: 8,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.03,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 7,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.03,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,おはよう
Dialogue: 8,0:13:14.03,0:13:14.82,Dial-CHI,,32,0,0,,你朋友？
Dialogue: 7,0:13:14.03,0:13:14.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,友達？
Dialogue: 8,0:13:14.82,0:13:15.89,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,B{\fscx50} {\fscx100}班的
Dialogue: 7,0:13:14.82,0:13:15.89,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,B{\fscx50} {\fscx100}組の
Dialogue: 8,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.26,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我是田汲
Dialogue: 7,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.26,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,田汲でーす
Dialogue: 8,0:13:17.26,0:13:19.20,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我是樱井
Dialogue: 7,0:13:17.26,0:13:19.20,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,桜井でーす
Dialogue: 8,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,回见
Dialogue: 7,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,またね
Dialogue: 8,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 7,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.33,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ねね
Dialogue: 8,0:13:24.58,0:13:27.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,毕业典礼那会儿  小泽跟你表白了吧
Dialogue: 7,0:13:24.58,0:13:27.96,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,卒業式のとき　小沢おざわに告られたんでしょ
Dialogue: 8,0:13:27.96,0:13:29.16,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 7,0:13:27.96,0:13:29.16,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なんで知ってんの？
Dialogue: 8,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.58,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,听小贵说的
Dialogue: 7,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.58,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,たかちゃんが言ってた
Dialogue: 8,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.08,Dial-CHI,,32,0,0,,不找个男朋友？
Dialogue: 7,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.08,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,彼氏作んないの？
Dialogue: 8,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.05,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 7,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.05,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,やー
Dialogue: 8,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 7,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.84,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どうだろ
Dialogue: 8,0:13:37.63,0:13:40.26,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,五一黄金周去哪玩了
Dialogue: 7,0:13:37.63,0:13:40.26,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ゴールデンウイーク　どこか行きました？
Dialogue: 8,0:13:40.26,0:13:42.46,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,哪都没去  高代老师呢
Dialogue: 7,0:13:40.26,0:13:42.46,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いやあ　こうだいさんは？
Dialogue: 8,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.47,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我也哪都没去
Dialogue: 7,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.47,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私も全然
Dialogue: 8,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.26,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你那个外甥女呢
Dialogue: 7,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.26,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ウワサのめいっ子ちゃんは？
Dialogue: 8,0:13:46.26,0:13:50.59,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不好意思  那段时间休刊给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 7,0:13:46.26,0:13:50.59,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,すみません　その節は休載でご迷惑おかけして
Dialogue: 8,0:13:50.59,0:13:51.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,没事儿
Dialogue: 7,0:13:50.59,0:13:51.80,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,全然
Dialogue: 8,0:13:51.80,0:13:54.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,平白捡了个假期  跟中奖一样
Dialogue: 7,0:13:51.80,0:13:54.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,降って湧いた休みでラッキーみたいな
Dialogue: 8,0:13:55.46,0:13:59.09,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,第二卷的封面  我们怎么推进
Dialogue: 7,0:13:55.46,0:13:59.09,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,で　2{\fscx50} {\fscx100}巻の表紙ですが　どう進めましょうか
Dialogue: 8,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.53,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,说到这个
Dialogue: 7,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.53,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,それなんですけど
Dialogue: 8,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我有想画的东西了
Dialogue: 7,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私　描きたいのがありまして
Dialogue: 8,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,说来听听
Dialogue: 7,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.38,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,聞きたいです
Dialogue: 8,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您随便听听就行
Dialogue: 7,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,聞き流してくださいね
Dialogue: 8,0:14:06.41,0:14:09.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,托尔和塞卡不是有个看地图的桥段吗
Dialogue: 7,0:14:06.41,0:14:09.96,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,トールとサイカが地図を見るシーンがあるでしょ
Dialogue: 8,0:14:09.96,0:14:10.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 7,0:14:09.96,0:14:10.49,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 8,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.66,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,就是那儿
Dialogue: 7,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.66,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そこをですね
Dialogue: 8,0:14:12.03,0:14:13.51,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,绘美里  运动服
Dialogue: 7,0:14:12.03,0:14:13.51,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,えみり　体操着
Dialogue: 8,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.29,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,哇  谢谢
Dialogue: 7,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.29,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あー　ありがとう
Dialogue: 8,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.63,Dial-CHI,,32,0,0,,洗了再还你？
Dialogue: 7,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.63,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,洗って返す？
Dialogue: 8,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.11,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不用  我第五节课要穿
Dialogue: 7,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.11,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,5{\fscx50} {\fscx100}限で着るから　いい
Dialogue: 8,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.51,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 7,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.51,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,助かったあ
Dialogue: 8,0:14:19.51,0:14:20.64,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 7,0:14:19.51,0:14:20.64,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どもー
Dialogue: 8,0:14:20.64,0:14:22.09,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 7,0:14:20.64,0:14:22.09,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どもー
Dialogue: 8,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,那咱们午休见
Dialogue: 7,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.50,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　お昼休み
Dialogue: 8,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 7,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.34,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お待たせー
Dialogue: 8,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,那群人可真够扎眼的
Dialogue: 7,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.04,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,派手だよね　あの軍団
Dialogue: 8,0:14:29.04,0:14:30.07,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 7,0:14:29.04,0:14:30.07,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ねー
Dialogue: 8,0:14:30.07,0:14:33.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,听说玉城初中的时候还被霸凌过
Dialogue: 7,0:14:30.07,0:14:33.56,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,玉城さんとか　中学のときいじめられてたのに
Dialogue: 8,0:14:34.13,0:14:35.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 7,0:14:34.13,0:14:35.02,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どの子
Dialogue: 8,0:14:35.02,0:14:36.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,短头发的
Dialogue: 7,0:14:35.02,0:14:36.31,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ショートの
Dialogue: 8,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,这回混进现充圈了  可以放心了
Dialogue: 7,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.86,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,今度は勝ち組か　安心だね
Dialogue: 8,0:14:40.86,0:14:43.28,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,话说  要是有她那张脸
Dialogue: 7,0:14:40.86,0:14:43.28,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ていうか　あの顔になれたら
Dialogue: 8,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.81,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,就算被霸凌我也认了
Dialogue: 7,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.81,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いじめられても全然ありだわ
Dialogue: 8,0:14:45.81,0:14:47.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 7,0:14:45.81,0:14:47.33,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,マジで？
Dialogue: 8,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.25,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 7,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.25,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 8,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,居然化妆了
Dialogue: 7,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お化粧してる
Dialogue: 8,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.14,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,开碰头会去了
Dialogue: 7,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.14,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,打ち合わせ
Dialogue: 8,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.40,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,还跟朋友喝了下午茶
Dialogue: 7,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.40,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あと　友達とお茶したり
Dialogue: 8,0:14:58.40,0:14:59.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,感觉你好像很累
Dialogue: 7,0:14:58.40,0:14:59.78,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なんか疲れてる？
Dialogue: 8,0:14:59.78,0:15:01.05,Dial-CHI,,32,0,0,,看出来了？
Dialogue: 7,0:14:59.78,0:15:01.05,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,分かる？
Dialogue: 8,0:15:01.05,0:15:02.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,毕竟说了很多话
Dialogue: 7,0:15:01.05,0:15:02.87,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いっぱいしゃべった
Dialogue: 8,0:15:02.87,0:15:04.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,笠町说要来
Dialogue: 7,0:15:02.87,0:15:04.56,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,笠町かさまちくん来るって言うし
Dialogue: 8,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,买完东西赶紧回家吧
Dialogue: 7,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.57,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,買い物して帰ろう
Dialogue: 8,0:15:05.57,0:15:07.35,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 7,0:15:05.57,0:15:07.35,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,やったー
Dialogue: 8,0:15:08.35,0:15:10.44,Dial-CHI,,32,0,0,,台湾？你要去？
Dialogue: 7,0:15:08.35,0:15:10.44,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,台湾？行くの？
Dialogue: 8,0:15:10.44,0:15:11.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是醍醐想去
Dialogue: 7,0:15:10.44,0:15:11.78,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,醍醐だいごがね
Dialogue: 8,0:15:11.78,0:15:14.48,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,目前还在做白日梦阶段
Dialogue: 7,0:15:11.78,0:15:14.48,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,まだ全然　妄想レベルだから
Dialogue: 8,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,高代小姐
Dialogue: 7,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.36,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,高代さん
Dialogue: 8,0:15:18.93,0:15:19.99,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 7,0:15:18.93,0:15:19.99,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 8,0:15:21.99,0:15:24.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我是后见监督人塔野
Dialogue: 7,0:15:21.99,0:15:24.65,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,後見監督人の塔野です
Dialogue: 8,0:15:24.65,0:15:28.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,办人身保险手续的时候  咱们见过一面
Dialogue: 7,0:15:24.65,0:15:28.12,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,生命保険の手続きの際にも　一度お会いしましたが
Dialogue: 8,0:15:28.12,0:15:30.81,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,有这回事吗
Dialogue: 7,0:15:28.12,0:15:30.81,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そうでしたっけ
Dialogue: 8,0:15:30.81,0:15:33.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不好意思  是我失礼了
Dialogue: 7,0:15:30.81,0:15:33.38,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,すみません　失礼しました
Dialogue: 8,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.03,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,请别放在心上
Dialogue: 7,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.03,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お気になさらず
Dialogue: 8,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.00,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,言归正传
Dialogue: 7,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.00,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,それよりも
Dialogue: 8,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.95,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我给您打过好几次电话
Dialogue: 7,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.95,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,何度かお電話差し上げたのですが
Dialogue: 8,0:15:42.95,0:15:44.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,难道您很忙吗
Dialogue: 7,0:15:42.95,0:15:44.38,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お忙しかったですか
Dialogue: 8,0:15:44.63,0:15:48.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,那个  我以为是骚扰电话
Dialogue: 7,0:15:44.63,0:15:48.18,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,その　知らない番号だと思って
Dialogue: 8,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.98,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,而且工作也忙
Dialogue: 7,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.98,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,仕事もありましたし
Dialogue: 8,0:15:49.98,0:15:51.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 7,0:15:49.98,0:15:51.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そうですか
Dialogue: 8,0:15:51.41,0:15:54.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,那我就开门见山了
Dialogue: 7,0:15:51.41,0:15:54.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,では　早速本題なのですが
Dialogue: 8,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 7,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.39,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 8,0:15:56.18,0:16:00.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,前几天  您提交了小朝名下的存折复印件
Dialogue: 7,0:15:56.18,0:16:00.37,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,先日ご提出いただいた　朝さん名義の通帳のコピー
Dialogue: 8,0:16:01.35,0:16:03.73,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不好意思  交得有点晚
Dialogue: 7,0:16:01.35,0:16:03.73,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,すみません　提出遅くなって
Dialogue: 8,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.83,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 7,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.83,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 8,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.28,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,请看这一项内容
Dialogue: 7,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.28,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,それのここなんですが
Dialogue: 8,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.98,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,4{\fscx50} {\fscx100}月{\fscx50} {\fscx100}30{\fscx50} {\fscx100}日
Dialogue: 7,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.98,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,4{\fscx50} {\fscx100}月{\fscx50} {\fscx100}30{\fscx50} {\fscx100}日
Dialogue: 8,0:16:08.98,0:16:11.53,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,取走了三十万现金
Dialogue: 7,0:16:08.98,0:16:11.53,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,30{\fscx50} {\fscx100}万円の現金が引き出されています
Dialogue: 8,0:16:12.62,0:16:15.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您能解释一下这笔钱的用途吗
Dialogue: 7,0:16:12.62,0:16:15.04,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,この用途をご説明くださいますか
Dialogue: 8,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.29,Dial-CHI,,32,0,0,,三… 三十万？
Dialogue: 7,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.29,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,さ… 30{\fscx50} {\fscx100}万？
Dialogue: 8,0:16:17.29,0:16:19.07,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是现金吗
Dialogue: 7,0:16:17.29,0:16:19.07,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,現金ですか
Dialogue: 8,0:16:19.07,0:16:20.09,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 7,0:16:19.07,0:16:20.09,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 8,0:16:20.09,0:16:23.05,Dial-CHI,,32,0,0,,从我姐姐姐夫的遗产账户里取的？
Dialogue: 7,0:16:20.09,0:16:23.05,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あ… 姉夫婦の遺産の口座から？
Dialogue: 8,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是的  我刚才已经说了
Dialogue: 7,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.92,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そうです　先ほど申し上げました
Dialogue: 8,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.83,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您还留着发票或收据吗
Dialogue: 7,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.83,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,レシートか領収書は残っていらっしゃいますか
Dialogue: 8,0:16:29.83,0:16:30.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 7,0:16:29.83,0:16:30.80,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 8,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.64,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,家庭记账本上有记录也行
Dialogue: 7,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.64,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,家計簿などのメモでも結構です
Dialogue: 8,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.95,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我以前跟您解释过
Dialogue: 7,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.95,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,以前にもご説明したはずですが
Dialogue: 8,0:16:36.95,0:16:39.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,这是您作为后见人的义务
Dialogue: 7,0:16:36.95,0:16:39.57,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,高代さんは後見人の義務として
Dialogue: 8,0:16:39.57,0:16:43.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,今后还请提交收支报告书
Dialogue: 7,0:16:39.57,0:16:43.02,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,今後　収支報告書も提出していただきますし
Dialogue: 8,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,那个还没…
Dialogue: 7,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.24,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,それはまだ…
Dialogue: 8,0:16:44.24,0:16:47.28,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,这次您寄送存折复印件的时候
Dialogue: 7,0:16:44.24,0:16:47.28,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,今回　通帳のコピーをお送りくださったときに
Dialogue: 8,0:16:47.28,0:16:50.15,Dial-CHI-TOP,,0,0,0,,我以为您肯定看过了
Dialogue: 7,0:16:47.28,0:16:50.15,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,当然チェックされたのではないかと思うのですが
Dialogue: 8,0:16:50.15,0:16:52.01,Dial-CHI-TOP,,0,0,0,,您该不会没看吧
Dialogue: 7,0:16:50.15,0:16:52.01,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,そうではないということでしょうか
Dialogue: 8,0:16:50.89,0:16:53.00,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您慢点
Dialogue: 7,0:16:50.89,0:16:53.00,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ちょ… ゆっくり
Dialogue: 8,0:16:53.00,0:16:55.29,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,麻烦您慢点说
Dialogue: 7,0:16:53.00,0:16:55.29,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ゆっくりしゃべってください
Dialogue: 8,0:16:56.15,0:16:59.54,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您这滔滔不绝  怪吓人的
Dialogue: 7,0:16:56.15,0:16:59.54,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,わーっと言われると　怖いので
Dialogue: 8,0:17:00.37,0:17:01.61,Dial-CHI,,32,0,0,,吓人？
Dialogue: 7,0:17:00.37,0:17:01.61,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,怖い？
Dialogue: 8,0:17:02.56,0:17:03.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 7,0:17:02.56,0:17:03.92,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,すみません
Dialogue: 8,0:17:04.47,0:17:05.67,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,账户里的钱
Dialogue: 7,0:17:04.47,0:17:05.67,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,このお金は
Dialogue: 8,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.27,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,除了她的学费和零花钱
Dialogue: 7,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.27,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,彼女の学費周りと小遣い以外
Dialogue: 8,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我完全没动过
Dialogue: 7,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.76,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ノータッチです
Dialogue: 8,0:17:09.76,0:17:12.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,生活费是从我的账户出的
Dialogue: 7,0:17:09.76,0:17:12.65,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,生活費は私の口座から
Dialogue: 8,0:17:12.65,0:17:13.68,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,零花钱
Dialogue: 7,0:17:12.65,0:17:13.68,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,小遣いも
Dialogue: 8,0:17:14.07,0:17:17.47,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是自动汇到她的账户里
Dialogue: 7,0:17:14.07,0:17:17.47,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,彼女の口座に自動送金されるようにしました
Dialogue: 8,0:17:17.47,0:17:18.81,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,因为我会忘
Dialogue: 7,0:17:17.47,0:17:18.81,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,忘れるから
Dialogue: 8,0:17:19.53,0:17:20.94,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 7,0:17:19.53,0:17:20.94,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そんなわけで
Dialogue: 8,0:17:20.94,0:17:25.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,实在抱歉  复印件我没看就寄过去了
Dialogue: 7,0:17:20.94,0:17:25.01,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,すみません　コピーはチェックせず送ってしまいました
Dialogue: 8,0:17:25.58,0:17:27.44,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,所以这三十万
Dialogue: 7,0:17:25.58,0:17:27.44,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,だから{\fscx50} {\fscx100}30{\fscx50} {\fscx100}万なんて
Dialogue: 8,0:17:27.75,0:17:29.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我也是一头雾水
Dialogue: 7,0:17:27.75,0:17:29.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,何が何やら
Dialogue: 8,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是我冒犯了
Dialogue: 7,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.80,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,失礼しました
Dialogue: 8,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,刚才用了质问般的语气
Dialogue: 7,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.71,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,確かに詰問するような調子でした
Dialogue: 8,0:17:35.71,0:17:36.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,毕竟
Dialogue: 7,0:17:35.71,0:17:36.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,その
Dialogue: 8,0:17:36.94,0:17:39.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我要保障孩子的权益
Dialogue: 7,0:17:36.94,0:17:39.78,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,子どもの人権が第一ですから
Dialogue: 8,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.83,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,话说得重了些
Dialogue: 7,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.83,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私もついムキに
Dialogue: 8,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.60,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,况且您又不接电话
Dialogue: 7,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.60,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,電話にもお出にならないし
Dialogue: 8,0:17:43.60,0:17:46.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我还以为您是个不靠谱的人
Dialogue: 7,0:17:43.60,0:17:46.34,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,とんでもない人ではないかと
Dialogue: 8,0:17:46.59,0:17:49.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是  我这人确实挺不靠谱的
Dialogue: 7,0:17:46.59,0:17:49.92,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,はい　とんでもない人で　ホント
Dialogue: 8,0:17:50.47,0:17:52.44,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,对不起  我又说错话了
Dialogue: 7,0:17:50.47,0:17:52.44,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,すみません　また失言を
Dialogue: 8,0:17:52.44,0:17:56.68,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,没事  我这人连一些简单的事都办不明白
Dialogue: 7,0:17:52.44,0:17:56.68,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いや　普通のことが普通にできない人間で
Dialogue: 8,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.97,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,电脑
Dialogue: 7,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.97,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,パソコン
Dialogue: 8,0:17:59.07,0:18:00.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我买了电脑
Dialogue: 7,0:17:59.07,0:18:00.84,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,パソコン　買いました
Dialogue: 8,0:18:00.84,0:18:02.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,苹果笔记本
Dialogue: 7,0:18:00.84,0:18:02.56,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,Mac{\fscx50} {\fscx100}のノートパソコン
Dialogue: 8,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是学校要用的教具吗
Dialogue: 7,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,それは学校の教材ですか
Dialogue: 8,0:18:05.82,0:18:07.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 7,0:18:05.82,0:18:07.34,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,違います
Dialogue: 8,0:18:07.34,0:18:10.47,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是别人非要你买的吗
Dialogue: 7,0:18:07.34,0:18:10.47,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,誰かに言われて買わなければならなかった？
Dialogue: 8,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 7,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.36,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,違います
Dialogue: 8,0:18:12.82,0:18:14.00,Dial-CHI,,32,0,0,,朝？
Dialogue: 7,0:18:12.82,0:18:14.00,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝？
Dialogue: 8,0:18:15.16,0:18:16.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 7,0:18:15.16,0:18:16.45,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 8,0:18:18.78,0:18:24.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我想着有了电脑  就能一个人搞音乐了
Dialogue: 7,0:18:18.78,0:18:24.04,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,パソコンがあったら　1{\fscx50} {\fscx100}人で音楽できるかなって
Dialogue: 8,0:18:24.04,0:18:27.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我怕你反对我加入轻音社
Dialogue: 7,0:18:24.04,0:18:27.50,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,軽音部　反対されるかもって
Dialogue: 8,0:18:28.24,0:18:29.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 7,0:18:28.24,0:18:29.65,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,だって
Dialogue: 8,0:18:29.65,0:18:30.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,小朝
Dialogue: 7,0:18:29.65,0:18:30.76,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝さん
Dialogue: 8,0:18:30.76,0:18:34.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,迄今为止  高代小姐限制过你的行为吗
Dialogue: 7,0:18:30.76,0:18:34.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,これまで高代さんに行動を制限されたことはありますか
Dialogue: 8,0:18:35.53,0:18:36.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 7,0:18:35.53,0:18:36.80,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ないです
Dialogue: 8,0:18:36.80,0:18:40.89,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你的感受只属于自己
Dialogue: 7,0:18:36.80,0:18:40.89,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あなたの感じ方はあなただけのものだから
Dialogue: 8,0:18:41.27,0:18:43.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,无论你怎么想
Dialogue: 7,0:18:41.27,0:18:43.02,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あなたがどう思おうと
Dialogue: 8,0:18:43.02,0:18:46.29,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,别人都没有资格指责你
Dialogue: 7,0:18:43.02,0:18:46.29,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,それを責める権利はない　誰にも
Dialogue: 8,0:18:46.29,0:18:48.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,完全没有
Dialogue: 7,0:18:46.29,0:18:48.15,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,全然ないです
Dialogue: 8,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,可她毕竟是大人
Dialogue: 7,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.15,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,でも　大人だから
Dialogue: 8,0:18:51.54,0:18:54.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我觉得她会反对
Dialogue: 7,0:18:51.54,0:18:54.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,反対されると思って
Dialogue: 8,0:18:54.76,0:18:56.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你要做你想做的人
Dialogue: 7,0:18:54.76,0:18:56.91,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なりたいものになりなさい
Dialogue: 8,0:18:57.37,0:19:01.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,总之我也说不清楚
Dialogue: 7,0:18:57.37,0:19:01.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なんか訳分かんなくなっちゃって
Dialogue: 8,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.27,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 7,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.27,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 8,0:19:04.96,0:19:08.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,朝  虽然有不少事要跟你说
Dialogue: 7,0:19:04.96,0:19:08.38,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝　話すべきことはいろいろあるけど
Dialogue: 8,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.75,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,留到下次吧
Dialogue: 7,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.75,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,今度にしよう
Dialogue: 8,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.00,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,去洗把脸
Dialogue: 7,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.00,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,顔洗っておいで
Dialogue: 8,0:19:17.68,0:19:23.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我跟她说过  想进轻音社进就是了
Dialogue: 7,0:19:17.68,0:19:23.02,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,軽音部に入りたいなら　入ればいいと言ったことがあります
Dialogue: 8,0:19:23.02,0:19:26.27,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,她说父母会不高兴
Dialogue: 7,0:19:23.02,0:19:26.27,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,彼女は親が喜ばないと
Dialogue: 8,0:19:26.27,0:19:29.44,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,看来她还在寻找自我
Dialogue: 7,0:19:26.27,0:19:29.44,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,自分を模索している最中のようです
Dialogue: 8,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,就算没有这件事
Dialogue: 7,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.45,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,こんな状況でなくても
Dialogue: 8,0:19:31.45,0:19:33.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,她也到了多愁善感的年纪
Dialogue: 7,0:19:31.45,0:19:33.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そういう年頃ですし
Dialogue: 8,0:19:36.18,0:19:39.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,要是有些事不方便跟高代小姐或学校说
Dialogue: 7,0:19:36.18,0:19:39.04,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,高代さんや学校に相談できないことがあれば
Dialogue: 8,0:19:39.04,0:19:40.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你就跟我说吧
Dialogue: 7,0:19:39.04,0:19:40.45,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私に相談してください
Dialogue: 8,0:19:41.23,0:19:42.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 7,0:19:41.23,0:19:42.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 8,0:19:42.41,0:19:44.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,无论什么事都可以
Dialogue: 7,0:19:42.41,0:19:44.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なんでもご相談に乗ります
Dialogue: 8,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我毕竟经验不足
Dialogue: 7,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.96,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私も経験不足でして
Dialogue: 8,0:19:46.96,0:19:51.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,很少有机会和您这号人打交道
Dialogue: 7,0:19:46.96,0:19:51.21,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あなたのようなタイプの方と接する機会がなかったものですから
Dialogue: 8,0:19:51.87,0:19:55.13,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我… 我这号人
Dialogue: 7,0:19:51.87,0:19:55.13,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,だっ　私のようなタイプ
Dialogue: 8,0:19:55.13,0:19:57.09,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不是的  我是说职业
Dialogue: 7,0:19:55.13,0:19:57.09,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,違います　ご職業とか
Dialogue: 8,0:19:57.89,0:19:59.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,电话也不接
Dialogue: 7,0:19:57.89,0:19:59.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,電話にも出ず
Dialogue: 8,0:19:59.41,0:20:02.03,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,提交文件非要拖到死线
Dialogue: 7,0:19:59.41,0:20:02.03,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,書類の提出も締め切り　直前
Dialogue: 8,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我会全力支持你们的生活的
Dialogue: 7,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.56,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,サポートします　お二人の生活を
Dialogue: 8,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.13,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 7,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.13,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ですから
Dialogue: 8,0:20:07.70,0:20:11.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,以后还请多多关照
Dialogue: 7,0:20:07.70,0:20:11.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,これからもどうぞよろしくお願いします
Dialogue: 8,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 7,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.18,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,こちらこそ
Dialogue: 8,0:20:19.06,0:20:21.20,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,笠町  欢迎
Dialogue: 7,0:20:19.06,0:20:21.20,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,笠町くん　いらっしゃい
Dialogue: 8,0:20:22.33,0:20:24.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,给你们带了点牡蛎
Dialogue: 7,0:20:22.33,0:20:24.39,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,牡蠣　おすそ分け
Dialogue: 8,0:20:24.39,0:20:25.95,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 7,0:20:24.39,0:20:25.95,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,はじめまして
Dialogue: 8,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.83,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我叫塔野  是个律师
Dialogue: 7,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.83,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,弁護士の塔野と申しますが
Dialogue: 8,0:20:28.30,0:20:30.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您是高代小姐的男友吗
Dialogue: 7,0:20:28.30,0:20:30.96,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,高代さんとお付き合いされてる方ですか
Dialogue: 8,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,Mac{\fscx50} {\fscx100}啊
Dialogue: 7,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.84,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,Mac{\fscx50} {\fscx100}ねえ
Dialogue: 8,0:20:35.84,0:20:38.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我买给她也行
Dialogue: 7,0:20:35.84,0:20:38.15,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,俺が買い取ってもいいけど
Dialogue: 8,0:20:38.15,0:20:41.53,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,那样就搞不清是谁的责任了
Dialogue: 7,0:20:38.15,0:20:41.53,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,それじゃ責任の所在が分からなくなる
Dialogue: 8,0:20:41.53,0:20:42.72,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 7,0:20:41.53,0:20:42.72,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,だな
Dialogue: 8,0:20:44.24,0:20:47.23,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,原来那人是律师啊
Dialogue: 7,0:20:44.24,0:20:47.23,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,しかし　弁護士さんか
Dialogue: 8,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.18,Dial-CHI,,32,0,0,,累了？
Dialogue: 7,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.18,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,疲れた？
Dialogue: 8,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.48,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 7,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.48,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そうね
Dialogue: 8,0:20:51.48,0:20:53.61,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,还挺累的
Dialogue: 7,0:20:51.48,0:20:53.61,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,わりと疲れたかも
Dialogue: 8,0:20:56.33,0:20:59.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你就当大型犬在蹭你吧
Dialogue: 7,0:20:56.33,0:20:59.24,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,大型犬にモフられてると思ってくれ
Dialogue: 8,0:21:00.36,0:21:01.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,伯恩山犬
Dialogue: 7,0:21:00.36,0:21:01.87,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,バーニーズ・マウンテン
Dialogue: 8,0:21:01.87,0:21:03.73,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,那种吗
Dialogue: 7,0:21:01.87,0:21:03.73,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そんなか
Dialogue: 8,0:21:03.73,0:21:07.60,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,说起来  前阵子我也这么搂过朝
Dialogue: 7,0:21:03.73,0:21:07.60,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そういえば　こないだ朝にも同じことをした
Dialogue: 8,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,原来是从你身上学的
Dialogue: 7,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.80,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あなたのスタイルだったか
Dialogue: 8,0:21:13.68,0:21:16.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,朝估计喜欢这个
Dialogue: 7,0:21:13.68,0:21:16.36,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,これ　たぶん朝が好きなやつ
Dialogue: 8,0:21:16.36,0:21:18.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,她偶尔会唱几句
Dialogue: 7,0:21:16.36,0:21:18.01,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,たまに歌ってんの
Dialogue: 8,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 7,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.38,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 8,0:21:19.38,0:21:20.79,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,小朝
Dialogue: 7,0:21:19.38,0:21:20.79,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝さん
Dialogue: 8,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.35,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你喜欢的乐队出场了
Dialogue: 7,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.35,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あなたの好きな人たち　出てる
Dialogue: 8,0:21:26.52,0:21:28.73,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,看吗  过来吧
Dialogue: 7,0:21:26.52,0:21:28.73,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,見る？おいで
Dialogue: 8,0:21:33.65,0:21:34.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,挤一挤
Dialogue: 7,0:21:33.65,0:21:34.57,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ぎゅうぎゅう
Dialogue: 8,0:21:34.57,0:21:35.78,Dial-CHI,,32,0,0,,你喜欢这个？
Dialogue: 7,0:21:34.57,0:21:35.78,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,これ　好きなの？
Dialogue: 8,0:21:36.65,0:21:37.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,这首歌的贝斯
Dialogue: 7,0:21:36.65,0:21:37.78,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,この曲のね
Dialogue: 8,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.11,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢
Dialogue: 7,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.11,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ベースが好き
Dialogue: 8,0:21:40.11,0:21:42.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,真行  品味不错嘛
Dialogue: 7,0:21:40.11,0:21:42.85,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,しぶ　目の付けどころがいい
Dialogue: 8,0:21:42.85,0:21:44.30,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 7,0:21:42.85,0:21:44.30,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,確かに
Dialogue: 8,0:21:46.47,0:21:47.66,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,槙生姨
Dialogue: 7,0:21:46.47,0:21:47.66,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,槙生ちゃん
Dialogue: 8,0:21:48.94,0:21:52.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我能加入轻音社吗
Dialogue: 7,0:21:48.94,0:21:52.31,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私　軽音部入っていい？
Dialogue: 8,0:21:52.84,0:21:54.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 7,0:21:52.84,0:21:54.42,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,もちろん
Dialogue: 8,0:21:54.42,0:21:56.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,做你想做的事吧
Dialogue: 7,0:21:54.42,0:21:56.80,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あなたの好きなようにしなさい
Dialogue: 8,0:21:57.75,0:22:00.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,嗯  我会的
Dialogue: 7,0:21:57.75,0:22:00.12,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,うん　そうする
Dialogue: 8,0:22:01.32,0:22:02.30,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,这段
Dialogue: 7,0:22:01.32,0:22:02.30,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ここ
Dialogue: 8,0:22:02.30,0:22:03.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,这段的贝斯
Dialogue: 7,0:22:02.30,0:22:03.85,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ここのベース
Dialogue: 8,0:22:04.70,0:22:07.06,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,还挺帅
Dialogue: 7,0:22:04.70,0:22:07.06,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,かっこいい
